Like many, I was a bit put off by the sound track. So I did some experimentation with muting and running another video in the background for sound.
My favorite so far is Barracuda ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PeMvMNpvB5M )
The main riff seems much more appropriate for the battle, and the Tagline tends to hit at relevant moments in the video.
Would probably want her first creature arrow to be a Barracuda instead of a manticore though.

snippet.textDisplay:
Visuals 10/10
Plot 5/10 (Vivian is loosing and dying and doesnt give a fuck be more serious pls)
Musik 0/10 (Good song but doesnt fit, for zendikar with adventure and stuff yeah that would fit)
Ending 3/10 (Showing Godzilla is fun and all but why not make the insect monster mutate into it showcasing a mechanic and make it more interesting. Even mutating into the card would be sweet)

All in all downvote not because the parts are bad srsly great job well done and the set is currently looking to be amazing, but because i trust you to fix these minor problems and make it even better
